						<p>Access a visual depiction of your continuous growth over time by taking advantage of Milestone's intuitive graphical features to generate charts and graphs of your progress.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class='col-start-2 col-end-12 sm:col-start-7 sm:col-end-12 lg:col-start-7 lg:col-end-10 flex flex-col'>
					<div class='flex mb-2'>
						<i class='fas fa-arrow-circle-down mr-5 mt-1'></i>
						<div class='m-0'><p class='font-bold text-sm lg:text-justifymb-2 sm:mb-3'>REPORT GENERATION</p>
